<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en-GB">
<head>
	<title>My Military Move</title>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="application/xhtml+xml; charset=utf-8" />
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
	<link href=' http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Sans' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
	<div id="header">
	  	<div id="logo">
		<%= link_to image_tag("icons/logo_small.png", :border=>0), root_url %>
		</div>
	</div>
    <div id="main">
	  
	    <div id="top">
		  	<div id="beta">	
			    <h2>We Need Beta Users!
			    Sign up today and get the next year free.</h2>
			  </div>
	    </div>
	  <div id="sidebar">
		<h1>Take A Tour</h1>
		<div id="subtitle">
		  <p>Organize your military move.</p>
		<p>
		  <ul>
			<li>itinerary</li>
			<li>calendar</li>
			<li>lists & notes</li>
			<li>neighborhood research</li>
			<li>home research</li>
			<li>school research</li>
		  </ul>
		</p>
		</div>
		  <div id="security">
			<%= image_tag("icons/security.png", :border=>0) %>
		  </div>
	  </div>
	  <div id="sidebar_two">

		<div id="video">
			<%= image_tag("icons/video_coming_soon.png", :border=>0) %>
			<div class="get_started"><%= link_to image_tag ("buttons/get_started.png", :border=>0), new_user_session_path %></div>	
		</div>
	  </div>

	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_left">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/move_dash.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_left_text">
		<h2>Move Dashboard</h2>
		<div class='left'>
			<p>Snapshot of your upcoming move. This overview shows you <span class="highlight">how many days until your move</span>, a <span class="highlight">preview of your calendar </span> and a count of your <span class="highlight">current lists, notes, neighborhoods, homes and schools</span>.</p>
			<p>Note: If you do not know your move date today go ahead and get started, you can always enter a placeholder.</p>
		</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_right">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/calendar.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_right_text">
		<h2>Calendar</h2>
			<div class="right">
				You may keep a calendar. Your spouse may keep one too! <span class="highlight">Here you can put all your move/travel dates in one place</span>. 
			</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_left">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/itinerary.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_left_text">
		<h2>Itinerary</h2>
		<div class='left'>
			<p>Ah, the move itinerary. Where are you going to stay and how are you going to get there? <span class="highlight">Develop a plan</span>, <span class="highlight">pinpoint the legs of the trip</span> and <span class="highlight">track the money you'll spend.</span> </p>
		</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_right">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/lists.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_right_text">
		<h2>Lists</h2>
		<div class='right'><p>Chuck that steno pad. <span class="highlight">Keep your lists in one location, online.</span> Check off your items as you go. </p>
			<p>Bonus: That "honey do" list for your active duty member; now they can access their "to do" list from anywhere,  including work.</p></div>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_left">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/notes.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_left_text">
		<h2>Notes</h2>
		  <p>
			It's pretty simple. <span class="highlight">Sometimes you just need to take a note</span>. Take it here, that way you can't lose it.
		  </p>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_right">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/neighborhoods.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_right_text">
		<h2>Neighborhoods</h2>
		  <p>
			First and foremost, where are you going to live? Start by researching neighborhoods in the area. <span class="highlight">You can track location, distance, travel time, the pro and cons and take notes</span>.
		  </p>
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_left">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/homes.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_left_text">
		<h2>Homes</h2>
		  <p>
			Once you narrow down a few neighborhoods it's time to start looking at homes. Track them too! <span class="highlight">Keep information about all houses you are considering in one location</span>. 
		  </p>
		  <p>
			Bonus: Is your spouse deployed or overseas? By using Militarymoveit.com to manage all your research they can log on and take a look from anywhere!
		  </p>	
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshots">
	  <div id="screenshot_right">
		<%= image_tag("screenshots/schools.png", :border=>0) %>
	  </div>
	  <div id="screenshot_right_text">
		<h2>Schools</h2>
		  Moving with children is tough, but one thing that can improve the transition is choosing a good school. Organize school research from daycare to high school. 
	  </div>
	</div>
	<div id="screenshot_footer">
		<%= link_to image_tag("icons/get_started_large.png", :border=>0), new_user_session_path %>
	</div>

    </div>
  
  </div>
</body>